8#include "nouveau_drm.h"

10struct nouveau_framebuffer {
11 struct drm_framebuffer base;
12 struct nouveau_bo *nvbo;
13 struct nvkm_vma vma;
14 u32 r_handle;
15 u32 r_format;
16 u32 r_pitch;
17 struct nvif_object h_base[4];
18 struct nvif_object h_core;
19};
20
21static inline struct nouveau_framebuffer *
22nouveau_framebuffer(struct drm_framebuffer *fb)
23{
24 return container_of(fb, struct nouveau_framebuffer, base);
25}
26
27int nouveau_framebuffer_init(struct drm_device *, struct nouveau_framebuffer *,
28 struct drm_mode_fb_cmd2 *, struct nouveau_bo *);
29
30struct nouveau_page_flip_state {
31 struct list_head head;
32 struct drm_pending_vblank_event *event;
33 int crtc, bpp, pitch, x, y;
34 u64 offset;
35};
36
37struct nouveau_display {
38 void *priv;
39 void (*dtor)(struct drm_device *);
40 int (*init)(struct drm_device *);
41 void (*fini)(struct drm_device *);
42
43 int (*fb_ctor)(struct drm_framebuffer *);
44 void (*fb_dtor)(struct drm_framebuffer *);
45
46 struct nvif_object disp;
47
48 struct drm_property *dithering_mode;
49 struct drm_property *dithering_depth;
50 struct drm_property *underscan_property;
51 struct drm_property *underscan_hborder_property;
52 struct drm_property *underscan_vborder_property;
53 /* not really hue and saturation: */
54 struct drm_property *vibrant_hue_property;
55 struct drm_property *color_vibrance_property;
56};
57
58static inline struct nouveau_display *
59nouveau_display(struct drm_device *dev)
60{
61 return nouveau_drm(dev)->display;
62}
